# The above is the last commit message of the draft/post
#
# The habit writing template is as follows:
# <<< MSG begins
# habit(ARTICLE-TYPE): SHORTENED-TITLE-STRING
#
# * state: ARTICLE-STATE
#
# * description: ONELINE-DESCRIPTION-FOR-THE-CHANGE
# <<< MSG ends
#
# ARTICLE-TYPE := draft | post
# ARTICLE-STATE := DRAFT-STATE | POST-STATE
# DRAFT-STATE := scaffolding | fledging | editing
# POST-STATE := polishing | reviewing
# And
# 1. TYPE and STATE nees to match.
# 2. title string and description are free-style strings.
#
# Ref: http://carltonf.github.io/post/writing-habit-and-tools